These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, social-worker, analyst, writer
1. the engineer is on the left of the writer##1
2. the social-worker is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Job   | analyst | social-worker | engineer | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, disaster, sports, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports | disaster | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, milk, mirinda
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | milk | hot-chocolate | coffee | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
