2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |    3     |   4    |
| Cigar   | dannemann | vegafina | pall-mall | montecristo |

